[{"Id": 1000051, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "The one who want that he should be with Mohammad (s) and his Ahlul-Baiyt (a) in the hereafter and those who want that at the time of death, in grave, barzakh, on the day of judgement, while giving account, on bridge of Seraat etc. if he desires that Allah (swt) should see him with mercy then he should recite this dua after every obligatory namaz…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jo shakhs chahta ho keh uska hashr Muhammad-e-Mustafa (s) aur unki Aal-e-Paak (a) ke saath ho aur woh hazraat maut, qabr, barzakh, qayaamat, hisaab, Pool-e-Seraat waghaira ke jaise ahem mauqo’n par khaas taur par us par nazr-e-rehmat farmaaye to is dua ko har namaz-e-waajib ke baad padh liya kare…", "UrduDescription": "جو شخص چاہتا ہو کہ اس کا حشر محمد مصطفٰیؐ اور ان کی آل پاکؑ کے ساتھ ہو اور وہ حضرات موت، قبر، برزخ، قیامت، حساب، پُلصراط وغیرہ کے جیسے اہم مواقع پر خاص طور پر اس پر نظر رحمت فرمایں تو اس دعا کو ہر نماز فریضہ کے بعد پڑھ لیا کرے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSig